question: Puncak Jaya, which is the highest peak in South East Asia and only place in south east asia where ice Glacier can be found is located in which among the following countries?
explanation: Puncak Jaya, which is the highest peak in South East Asia and only place in south east asia where ice Glacier can be found is located in Indonesia. Other summits are East Carstensz Peak, Sumantri and Ngga Pulu.
